{"word":"ἀμαρύσσω","slug":"ἀμαρύσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμαρύσσω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Root <el>ΑΜΑΡΥΓ</el>, like <a href='S:μαρμαίρω'><el>μαρμαίρω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to sparkle, glance</i>, of the eye, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> of light, colour, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}